{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView\/TextView\/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)"},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@CM@CodeEditTextView@objc(cs)TextView(im)fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyphForPoint:","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"for"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"NSPoint","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"CodeEditTextView","title":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"CodeEditTextView"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the fraction of the distance from the left side of the character to the right side that a given point"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"lies."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/codeedittextview\/textview\/fractionofdistancethroughglyph(for:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView","doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView\/TextView","doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView\/TextView\/NSTextInputClient-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"for"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"point","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"NSPoint","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The point to test.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"point"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The fraction of the distance aPoint is through the glyph in which it lies. May be 0 or 1 if aPoint","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is not within the bounding rectangle of a glyph (0 if the point is to the left or above the glyph;","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"1 if it’s to the right or below).","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For purposes such as dragging out a selection or placing the insertion point, a partial percentage less than or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"equal to 0.5 indicates that aPoint should be considered as falling before the glyph; a partial percentage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"greater than 0.5 indicates that it should be considered as falling after the glyph. If the nearest glyph doesn’t"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"lie under aPoint at all (for example, if aPoint is beyond the beginning or end of a line), this ratio is 0 or 1."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For example, if the glyph stream contains the glyphs “A” and “b”, with the width of “A” being 13 points, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"aPoint is 8 points from the left side of “A”, then the fraction of the distance is 8\/13, or 0.615. In this","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"case, the aPoint should be considered as falling between “A” and “b” for purposes such as dragging out a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection or placing the insertion point.","type":"text"}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://CodeEditTextView/documentation/CodeEditTextView/TextView/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)":{"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the fraction of the distance from the left side of the character to the right side that a given point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"lies.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/codeedittextview\/textview\/fractionofdistancethroughglyph(for:)","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"for","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint","text":"NSPoint","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView\/TextView\/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)","title":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)"},"doc://CodeEditTextView/documentation/CodeEditTextView/TextView/NSTextInputClient-Implementations":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/codeedittextview\/textview\/nstextinputclient-implementations","role":"collectionGroup","title":"NSTextInputClient Implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView\/TextView\/NSTextInputClient-Implementations"},"doc://CodeEditTextView/documentation/CodeEditTextView":{"url":"\/documentation\/codeedittextview","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/CodeEditTextView\/documentation\/CodeEditTextView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A text editor designed to edit code documents."}],"title":"